---
title: Smoked Tofu Tacos with Mango Slaw and Cilantro-Lime Crema
description: Few things look as colourful as these tacos - with smoked tofu inside no less! There’s a hint of sweet mango amidst the expected tang of sour cream we all know and love. Top these tacos with a creamy avocado and you’ll be in for a sweet ride.
